<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hmmm, everyone seems to be really positave about this weapon, I hate to ruin your moods but this is the worst weapon I have ever had, I had a SBH before it and I am still wondering why I ever switched, Sure it hits for a good amount, but I miss and miss and in the end its not worth it, When i had my SBH I could go a battle with missing only 3 or 4 times, with this thing I can miss up to 8 times in a row and thats just in the beginning, its a good thing Paladins get Root because when something is running I cant ever kill it before it trains, not with this thing, So who ever came up with this Blackend Iron Butter Knife can suck wind because this sword blows!</font></td></tr></table>
