<BR>
While I would first recommend you not choose between 1HS and 2HS and instead level them both (my BAR/WAR found this out the hard way when I picked up a LoW cheap and had a 2HS of 32) much of the answer to your question depends on which of the two big Paladin weapons you want...and when.  Most don't have time to go after both a Ghoulsbane (1HS) AND a Soulfire (2HS) as cool as it might be.  For me, though, I frankly would hang on to the claws and try my level best to save enough to buy a BIBS too.  I love the fool thing.<BR>
