This weapon just does not sell. I was auctioning for ages, eventually sold it for 200 only to see the buyer trying to sell it for 250 afterwards. Oh well, great weapon after 20, nice damage, was hitting for 48's quite consistently whereas my Runic Carver max's about 44 and that's rare. Prefer the Carver due to the speed (and look) but below 20 I'd go for a Axe of the Iron Back if or SBH if you're limited on Plat.<BR>
